---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'

const yearsExperience = new Date().getFullYear() - 2007
---

<Layout title="About Tom Gooden">
  <div class="about container">
    <header>
      <div>
        <img alt="Who even are you" src="/images/parks-and-rec-craig-who-even-are-you.gif" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h1>About me</h1>
        <p>
          My name is Tom Gooden and I'm a Michigan based Developer and
          Designer who specializes in custom solutions for businesses
          including internal tooling and customer facing applications.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="about-main">
      <p>
        I'm a user-experience junkie, and for the past {yearsExperience}+ years I've been professionally
        creating websites and applications for businesses and governments of
        all sizes. My passion is coming up with ideas to make processes more
        efficient utilizing the JAMstack. You can usually catch me hanging out
        in the{' '}
        <a href="https://discord.gg/KntFa9p" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
          CodeHelp discord server
        </a>.
      </p>
      <div class="blocks">
        <div>
          <span>{`<code/help>`}</span>
          <a class="button" href="https://discord.gg/KntFa9p" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
            Join
          </a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>
            Here is a list of goodies I've compiled that I use in design,
            development, and just everyday life.
          </p>
          <a class="button" href="/uses/">Uses</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>A little more...</h2>
      <p>
        Above all else I am a Dad to 3 kids and{' '}
        <span class="strike">2</span> <span class="strike">3</span> 5
        dogs. During my downtime I like to learn new things that help expand
        my development skill-set, comic and MTG collecting, spending time
        outside, fishing and camping.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 899px) {
    .about {
      padding-top: 3rem;
    }
  }

  header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 425px 1fr;
    gap: 100px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 899px) {
    header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  }

  header img {
    border-radius: 40px 0 40px 0;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 899px) {
    .about h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size__h3);
    }
  }

  .about h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size__h4);
  }

  .blocks {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 899px) {
    .blocks {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  .blocks > div {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-size: var(--font-size__base--sm);
    gap: 30px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 899px) {
    .blocks > div {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .blocks > div :global(.button) {
      width: 100%;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  .blocks > div:nth-of-type(1) {
    background: rgba(245, 45, 134, 0.1);
    color: rgb(245, 45, 134);
  }

  .blocks > div:nth-of-type(1) span {
    font-family: var(--font-family__code);
    font-size: var(--font-size__h4);
  }

  .blocks > div:nth-of-type(2) {
    background: rgba(113, 28, 180, 0.1);
    color: rgb(113, 28, 180);
  }

  .blocks > div:nth-of-type(2) a {
    background: rgb(113, 28, 180);
    font-family: var(--font-family__code);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .blocks p {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
